My dog and I are synchronized 😂

#polotheschnauzer #minischnauzer #trainingdog #funnydogs #dogsofinstagram #love #funny #puppy

POLO ❤️

Thank you Carmen for capturing his first horse show!
Denny is ready for what’s to come 🖤✨
Galáctico and I really enjoyed todays shoot for @esstockholm thank you so much! 🧡
A very happy Denny with his new halter 🤩
As season approaches Denny and Galáctico put their game faces on. Let’s do this @julie_g_mcallister @didiamendolara !!! 🖤🧡
@pbequineclinic capturing a powerful moment between Galáctico and I! 🧡
Denny better than ever in our first outing of 2023! ✨🖤 No words to describe todays feeling! Hard work always pays off 🙏
What a day! Galáctico and I won todays very competitive PSG class 🥇with a PB of 73.5%!!! 🌟 He was just fantastic 🧡

Denny was just on fire last night! He is feeling amazing 🔥💪 Sadly that also cost us 3 very expensive mistakes but we still managed to score 72% and place top 8 among some of the best combinations! Looking forward to the next! 🖤✨

What a super day for Galáctico and I! We scored 68.6% in todays I1 and finished 7th out of a large and very competitive field of 23! We also marked a new PB! I can’t believe that Galáctico arrived not long ago and one judge scored us with a 70.2%! Very exciting 🧡

Galáctico was an absolute star in todays Nations Cup PSG! We scored so close to 68%, two of the judges scored us nearly 70%, and another PB!!! The journey 🙏
 
Thank you @didiamendolara @christinefirmindidot for trusting me with your boy! 🧡

Today Galáctico and I got another new PB of 70.8%!

This week has been incredible, two new PB and the most amount of 7.5s and 8s I have ever gotten 🙏

Thank you Didi and Christine for everything!

And thank you Galáctico for trusting me to ride you so competitively without knowing each other that much 🫶

What the perfect tack box looks like ✨
Thank you Joe and team!!!
Moments like these you realize your dreams came true ✨🖤
Denny placed top 9 in todays super competitive and large 4* GP! I’m so proud of how far you’ve come and thankful for the places you’ve taken me 🖤✨ Can’t wait for tomorrow night!

What a night, what a horse! Denny and I placed 5th in tonight’s 4* GPF one point away from podium! Today we were able to take into the ring our best version of the canter work, consistently sitting over 73%. Happy is an understatement. Thank you Denny, you are a fighter. And last but definitely not least thank you @julie_g_mcallister and @cdmcallister24 for the unconditional support and standing behind us, it means the world to me ✨🖤
Denny really loves the crowd! Thank you! 🖤✨
Galáctico made his small GP (I2) debut and won with a 72.9%!!! Feels a bit surreal at the moment 🙏💪🥇✨🧡
Galáctico starting to get ready for the big GP ⭐️

Galácticos GP debut is in the books!!! 🧡

What a special day for everyone. 

Congratulations Didi and Christine on officially owning a GP horse 🥳

Dad and brother thinking of you on this special day ❤️ 

For me its another step towards one of my dreams, another presented and debuted GP horse ✨

And last but not least thank you Galáctico for being such a fighter and the best partner, I can’t believe it’s only been 4 months 🧡
A very happy Denny! Yes, I have ridden those bucks 😬

GP world entered 🧡✅

Thank you so much for this amazing picture Carmen!

Welcome to this world Thyssen! 🤎🌙

Thyssen (x Ferderaux) was born some hours ago and his muscles already look like he has been in training for years! 

Sometimes you need a glimpse at the future, and this one looks bright!

My first colt, thank you father for this surprise!
Less is more even on a gentle giant 🤎
Never forget why we truly do this 🤍🐴
Two very different horses looking very similar 🩵
Thyssen has a huge personality, and canter! 🤩
As CHIO Aachen approaches, can’t help to take a trip down memory lane! Can’t believe I was 18 at the time 🧡
Show jumping times with the best pony in the world, Georgian de Milhas 🤍

Only A Kiss Will Break This Spell 💋 

#dressagehorse
Who needs bags when you can have saddles? Thank you Hermés! 🧡
It’s not a job. It’s not a hobby. It’s a form of life 🩷
After many years today I rode Don Diego for the first time, it was a beautiful full circle moment as we found a match in each other 🖤 Thank you brother for allowing me to ride him!
Friday night stars indeed, you’re a star ✨🖤
Aachen is always special, but even more if it’s passed through generations ♾️
Palm Beach vibes or Barbie fever? 🩷
What if it turns out better than you ever imagined? 💭
We‘ve all had a chilly pepper before 🌶️ 20 year old Alminar still feeling himself!
Got it all out but it took several hours and wasn’t sure if I wanted to laugh or to cry in the process of it 🫠

Welcome Sir Rubin!!!

Today was a very special day. After a lot of hard work I finally purchased my first horse! But not just any horse, I have searched for a long time waiting for something special, and when you know you know! Life has a way to handle timings and today our paths finally meet. There is nothing more rewarding than to be able to make your own dreams come true.

I couldn’t be happier to have @didiamendolara as my partner in this adventure, it means so much to me to be able to work with people I can call friends.

Last but not least, I want to thank @manuel_jjh for the wonderful job he has done training Rubin from a young horse to GP and for handing the reins over to me.

Cant wait to see what 2024 holds ✨
Douglas owned by Abby Laukka-Hardy in todays training 🤎
Sound on for the best comments (Yes I’m very romantic) 😂 So much love for this big guy 🤎 Love posting the piaffe, it’s so fun and playful!
Important things are ahead for Denny 💪🖤✨
After many years it’s gym time again 💪 big goals ahead
